/li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>A propriedade&nbsp;<strong><code>Number.NaN</code></strong> representa Not-A-Number (Não-Número). Equivalente a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p>Você não precisa criar um objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a> para acessar esta propriedade estática&nbsp;(use <code>Number.NaN</code>).</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"header\" colspan=\"2\">Property attributes of <code>Number.NaN</code></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Writable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Enumerable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Configurable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Detalhes</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%201st%20edition,%20June%201997.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n   <td>Definição Inicial. Implementado no JavaScript 1.1.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.7.3.4\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Number.NaN' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">